        }

        {
            //printf("%d\n",n);

            //printf("%s",string_input);

                //printf("hello\n");
                for(k=0;k<n;k++)
                {
                    //printf("ujjwal\n");
                    if(found==1)
                    {
                        break;
                    }
                    if(grid_matrix[j][k]==string_input[0])
                    {
                        check=word_search(j,k);
                        //printf("hello\n");
                        if(check==1)
                        {
                            found=1;
                        }
                    }
                    else if(grid_matrix[j][k] - 32 == string_input[0])
                    {
                        check=word_search(j,k);
                        //printf("hello\n");
                        if(check==1)
                        {
                            found=1;
                        }
                    }
                    else if(grid_matrix[j][k] + 32 == string_input[0])
                    {
                        check=word_search(j,k);
                        //printf("hello\n");
                        if(check==1)
                        {
                            found=1;
                        }
                    }
                }
                if(found==1)
                    break;
            }
        }
        printf("\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
